**File:** wait.ipd

**Shows:** Wait Elements, timeout wait type

**Components:** Start Element, Wait Element, End Element

A very simple process which enters a Wait Element, waits for 5 seconds, then continues.

Before it starts waiting and after it finished, it logs a message.
